@startuml Manage Products Schema - Very Simple
!theme plain
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #E3F2FD
  BorderColor #1976D2
}
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center

title Schema - Valdyti produktus (Paprasčiausia versija)

' ============================================
' AKTORIUS
' ============================================
actor "Šeimos narys" as User

' ============================================
' UI BOUNDARIES (Langai)
' ============================================
rectangle "Inventoriaus langas" <<boundary>> as InventoryPage
rectangle "Produkto pridėjimo langas" <<boundary>> as AddProductPage
rectangle "Produkto kortelės langas" <<boundary>> as ProductDetailPage

' ============================================
' CONTROLLER (Flutter BLoC)
' ============================================
rectangle "InventoryBloc\n(BLoC)" <<control>> as InventoryBloc

' ============================================
' EXTERNAL BOUNDARIES
' ============================================
rectangle "Supabase API" <<boundary>> as Supabase
rectangle "Open Food Facts API" <<boundary>> as OpenFoodAPI
rectangle "Mobile Scanner" <<boundary>> as BarcodeScanner
rectangle "Image Picker\n(Kamera/Galerija)" <<boundary>> as ImagePicker

' ============================================
' ENTITIES
' ============================================
rectangle "Product" <<entity>> as Product
rectangle "InventoryItem" <<entity>> as InventoryItem

' ============================================
' PAGRINDINIAI RYŠIAI
' ============================================

' User → UI Boundaries
User --> InventoryPage
User --> AddProductPage
User --> ProductDetailPage

' UI Boundaries → Controller
InventoryPage --> InventoryBloc
AddProductPage --> InventoryBloc
ProductDetailPage --> InventoryBloc

' Controller → External Boundaries
InventoryBloc --> Supabase
InventoryBloc --> OpenFoodAPI
InventoryBloc --> BarcodeScanner
InventoryBloc --> ImagePicker

' Controller → Entities
InventoryBloc --> Product
InventoryBloc --> InventoryItem

' External Boundaries → Controller (atsakymai)
Supabase --> InventoryBloc
OpenFoodAPI --> InventoryBloc
BarcodeScanner --> InventoryBloc
ImagePicker --> InventoryBloc

' Controller → UI Boundaries (atsakymai)
InventoryBloc --> InventoryPage
InventoryBloc --> AddProductPage
InventoryBloc --> ProductDetailPage

note bottom
  **SCHEMA SANTRAUKA:**
  
  **3 UI Boundaries** (Langai)
  **1 Controller** (InventoryBloc - Flutter BLoC)
  **4 External Boundaries** (Išorinės sistemos)
  **2 Entities** (Product, InventoryItem)
  
  **Kaip veikia:**
  User → UI Boundary → Controller → External Boundary/Entity
  External Boundary/Entity → Controller → UI Boundary → User
end note

@enduml



























